\phi(x, y) = x + ye^{\frac{x}{y}} + w(y)
\frac{\partial \phi}{\partial y} = e^{\frac{x}{y}}(1 - \frac{x}{y^2}) + \frac{\partial w}{\partial y}
\frac{\partial \phi}{\partial y} = \mathbf{V}_y
\frac{\partial w}{\partial y} = 0
